# 🚀 My Arduino + Firebase Project

This project uses ESP32 and Firebase to read sensor data and send it to the cloud.

---

## 🎬 Demo Video

👉 [Watch on YouTube Shorts](https://youtube.com/shorts/6BPG1ipkBdA?feature=share)

---

## 📦 Required Libraries

Make sure to install the following libraries via the Arduino Library Manager:

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/mobizt/Firebase-ESP-Client"><code>Firebase_ESP_Client</code></a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/beegee-tokyo/DHTesp"><code>DHT sensor library for ESPx</code></a></li>
</ul>

